quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,123,"Eehey mon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe, ka…ďee …ďeen …ďa…óii…ďe on immorde e heefer…ďe …ďeen; yo …ďe taw e moo…óon √Īaa…óre. ngnndon pellet Alla no won di e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen."
  9,124,"Si cortewol(simoore) jippinaama, hino e ma…ď…ďe on wi'oowo : "ko hommbo e mo'on woni ko ngol …ďeydi gooŇč…óinal?" Ammaa …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, ngol …ďeydu …ďe gooŇč…óinal, kam…ďe he…ďe mbeltoo."
  9,125,"Ammma …ďeen …ďeen √Īawu woni ka …ďer…óe muen, ngol …ďeydu …ďe so…ďe e hoore so…ďe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe maayi ko …ďe heefer…ďe."
  9,126,"E …ďee njiaani won de kam…ďe he…ďe njarribee hitaande kala laawol maa laa…ďi …ói…ói? refti …ďe tuubataa, …ďe ngonnah waactotoo…ďe."
  9,127,"Si tawii cortewol jippinaama, yoga ma…ď…ďe ndaara yoga […ďe mbi'a] : "Hara go…ó…óo no yi*a on?" refti …ďe ha…ďana=pirlito. Alla firlitii …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe tawde ko …ďe yim…ďe …ďe paamataa."
  9,128,"Mi woo…óndi nulaa…óo arii e moo…óon, jeyaa…óo emon hino sa…óta e makko ko tampoton, deer…óu…óo e moo…óon, newanii…óo hinnotoo…óo(yurmotoodo) gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  9,129,"Si …ďe huccitii(nduŇčtiima), maaku : "Alla yonii kam. Alaa dewetee…óo si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko e makko mi fawii; ko KaŇčko woni Jey…óo daŇčkii mawnu…óo on"."